{
  "text": "I planned to redraw the Tarot cards, eliminating extraneous additions by those who came after Raw's initial given and would like to quickly go through those things that I intend to eliminate from each card we've gone over. Ask Raw if there's anything else that should be eliminated. Make the cards as they were when they were originally drawn before the astrological and other appendages were added. I would eliminate all of the letters around the edge of the card, with the possible exception of the number of the card. One, two, three, etc. That would be the case for all of the cards, the exterior lettering and numbering. In card number one, I would eliminate the star at the upper right-hand corner. Eliminate the wand, the magician's hand. I understand that the sphere remains. I'm not sure where it should be. Would Rakama comment on that, please? Hi. The elimination of letters is acceptable. Secondly, the illumination of stars is acceptable in all cases. Thirdly, the elimination of the wand is appropriate, a fourthly the a sphere may be a scene to a be held a by the thumb and index and second a finger. Fifthly, we would note that it is not possible to offer what you may call a pure deck if you would use this term of tahol, a due to the fact that when these images were first on there was all ready distortion in various and asundry ways are mostly cultural. A sixthly, although it is a good to view the images without the astrological auditions, it is to be noted that the more general positions, phases, and characteristics of each concept complex are those which are significant.",
  "timestamps": {
    "segment": [
      {
        "segment": "I planned to redraw the Tarot cards, eliminating extraneous additions by those who came after Raw's initial given and would like to quickly go through those things that I intend to eliminate from each card we've gone over.",
        "start_offset": 36,
        "end_offset": 415,
        "start": 2.88,
        "end": 33.2
      },
      {
        "segment": "Ask Raw if there's anything else that should be eliminated.",
        "start_offset": 429,
        "end_offset": 469,
        "start": 34.32,
        "end": 37.52
      },
      {
        "segment": "Make the cards as they were when they were originally drawn before the astrological and other appendages were added.",
        "start_offset": 473,
        "end_offset": 635,
        "start": 37.84,
        "end": 50.800000000000004
      },
      {
        "segment": "I would eliminate all of the letters around the edge of the card, with the possible exception of the number of the card.",
        "start_offset": 643,
        "end_offset": 783,
        "start": 51.44,
        "end": 62.64
      },
      {
        "segment": "One, two, three, etc.",
        "start_offset": 803,
        "end_offset": 824,
        "start": 64.24,
        "end": 65.92
      },
      {
        "segment": "That would be the case for all of the cards, the exterior lettering and numbering.",
        "start_offset": 860,
        "end_offset": 917,
        "start": 68.8,
        "end": 73.36
      },
      {
        "segment": "In card number one, I would eliminate the star at the upper right-hand corner.",
        "start_offset": 924,
        "end_offset": 988,
        "start": 73.92,
        "end": 79.04
      },
      {
        "segment": "Eliminate the wand, the magician's hand.",
        "start_offset": 992,
        "end_offset": 1034,
        "start": 79.36,
        "end": 82.72
      },
      {
        "segment": "I understand that the sphere remains.",
        "start_offset": 1039,
        "end_offset": 1069,
        "start": 83.12,
        "end": 85.52
      },
      {
        "segment": "I'm not sure where it should be.",
        "start_offset": 1073,
        "end_offset": 1107,
        "start": 85.84,
        "end": 88.56
      },
      {
        "segment": "Would Rakama comment on that, please?",
        "start_offset": 1110,
        "end_offset": 1145,
        "start": 88.8,
        "end": 91.60000000000001
      },
      {
        "segment": "Hi.",
        "start_offset": 1197,
        "end_offset": 1201,
        "start": 95.76,
        "end": 96.08
      },
      {
        "segment": "The elimination of letters is acceptable.",
        "start_offset": 1299,
        "end_offset": 1441,
        "start": 103.92,
        "end": 115.28
      },
      {
        "segment": "Secondly, the illumination of stars is acceptable in all cases.",
        "start_offset": 1464,
        "end_offset": 1707,
        "start": 117.12,
        "end": 136.56
      },
      {
        "segment": "Thirdly, the elimination of the wand is appropriate, a fourthly the a sphere may be a scene to a be held a by the thumb and index and second a finger.",
        "start_offset": 1750,
        "end_offset": 2335,
        "start": 140.0,
        "end": 186.8
      },
      {
        "segment": "Fifthly, we would note that it is not possible to offer what you may call a pure deck if you would use this term of tahol, a due to the fact that when these images were first on there was all ready distortion in various and asundry ways are mostly cultural.",
        "start_offset": 2398,
